# Window Crank Project - Header Files

This directory contains the header files for the Window Crank servo control system.

## Files

### servo.h
ESP32 servo control interface using LEDC PWM peripheral. Provides precise microsecond pulse width control for standard servo motors.

### display.h
OLED display interface for SSD1306 128x64 displays. Shows real-time servo position, pulse width, and button status using U8g2 library.

### bleComm.h
BLE communication interface for Flutter app integration. Handles position commands and notification data via NimBLE stack.

## Usage

Include headers in your source files:

```cpp
#include "servo.h"
#include "display.h"
#include "bleComm.h"
```

## Dependencies

- Arduino.h (ESP32 core)
- U8g2lib.h (OLED display library)

